<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    
    <h2>{{ t "about.what-can-i-do.title" }}</h2>

      <dl>
        <dt>Demand action from the Mayor!</dt>
        <dd><a href='/take-action'>Click here</a> for the phone number of the Mayor's office, and a script detailing what to say.</dd>
      </dl>

      <dl>
        <dt>Get involved</dt>
        <dd>There are several activist organizations working to eliminate the petcoke hazard from our communities</dd>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <a href='https://www.facebook.com/pages/Chicago-South-East-Side-Coalition-To-Ban-Petcoke/848330295223606?fref=ts' target='_blank'>
